# CSS Extraction Walkthrough

## What Changed

### [NEW] [tokens.css](file:///d:/Paul/prototypes/styles/tokens.css)
Shared design-system layer extracted from [globals.css](file:///d:/Paul/prototypes/kpi-admin-login/src/app/globals.css). Contains:
- `:root` + `[data-theme="dark"]` CSS variables
- `*` reset, `body` base, skip-to-content
- Mode toggle (`.mode-toggle`, `.toggle-pill`, `.toggle-icon`)
- Buttons (`.btn-outline`, `.btn-primary`, loading states)
- Inputs (`.input-group`, `.input-wrapper`, validation states)
- Spinner + `@keyframes rotation`
- Divider, icon-btn, forgot-password link
- All `prefers-reduced-motion` rules for shared elements

### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///d:/Paul/prototypes/kpi-admin-login/src/app/globals.css)
Slimmed from **~970 → ~470 lines**. Now contains only layout-specific classes:
- `.layout-wrapper`, `.layout-split`, `.layout-form-side`, `.layout-illustration-side`
- `.header`, `.logo`, `.btn-back`
- `.main-content`, `.headline`, `.subtitle`, `.login-container`
- `.footer-wrapper`, `.footer-text`
- `.input-footer`, `.status-text` (layout wrappers)
- All responsive `@media` breakpoints for the above

